gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 110, Spurs 105
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Nikola Jokics 42 points, 16 rebounds and six assists, the Nuggets defeated the Spurs, 110-105. Aaron Gordon (23 points, seven rebounds, four assists) and Michael Porter Jr. (15 points, career-high 16 rebounds) added a combined 38 points for the Nuggets in the victory, while Victor Wembanyama tallied 23 points, 15 rebounds, eight assists and nine blocks for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Nuggets have won back-to-back games as they improve to 53-23 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 18-58.
